/**
 * isEmailValid()
 * ----------------
 * Simple helper function to validate an email address.
 * Uses a basic regular expression to ensure the format:
 *   - Some characters before '@'
 *   - Domain name after '@'
 *   - A dot (.) followed by a valid extension
 *
 * @param {string} email - The email string to validate
 * @returns {boolean} true if email is in a valid format
